*linux-gpib-3.2.15 (31 Jan 2011)

  31 Jan 2011; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org>
  +linux-gpib-3.2.15.ebuild, +files/linux-gpib-3.2.15-build.patch,
  +metadata.xml:
